text:
I don't want to call this genre self-help because, nowadays, books in that genre have become the same repetitive thing.

But there are books like How to Win Friends and Influence People that are mentioned over and over again on HN comments.

Have you implemented advice from any such book that have impacted your life for the better? How did it affect your well being?
